OL,3,CEnvironmental campaigners visit south
OL,4,Cof Scotland for riverside clean-up
OL,6,F'Keep Scotland Beautiful' joined
OL,7,Fpeople in Lockerbie for a community
OL,8,Fclean-up along the river Annan as part
OL,9,Fof a national campaign to tackle water
OL,10,Fpollution.
OL,12,FThe environmental group's 'Upstream
OL,13,FBattle' campaign aims to spread
OL,14,Fawareness of marine litter and
OL,15,Fencourage people to understand the
OL,16,Fimportance of keeping their rivers
OL,17,Fclean.
