OL,3,CEnvironmental campaigners visit south
OL,4,Cof Scotland for riverside clean-up
OL,6,FA litter pick and litter survey took
OL,7,Fplace on along River Annan in
OL,8,FLockerbie on Sunday morning, and the
OL,9,Fdata collected will contribute to a
OL,10,Fnational database which will give a
OL,11,Fpicture of the problem areas and
OL,12,Fhotspots across the country.JThose
OL,13,Fareas can then be targeted with the
OL,14,Faim of stopping Scotland's waterways,
OL,15,Fmarine environments, and ecosystems
OL,16,Ffrom being polluted with rubbish
OL,17,Fdumped on land.
